{"tid":1562160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(中国豬買不起？)  官媒：對身體不好應少吃","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:10:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf4d9a879b355478a38fc2f87a97e42eefc1720","tid":1562160,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟疫情肆虐中國，豬肉價格持續飆漲，日前中國官方公佈數據顯示，中國豬肉價格8月急升46%，推動8月CPI（居民消費價格指數）上漲約1.08個百分點。為因應豬肉短缺危機，中國官媒近日刊文呼籲民眾應改變飲食習慣少吃豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》報導，穩定豬價被中國官方視為「政治任務」，為因應豬肉價格暴漲，中國官媒《環球時報》旗下的《生命時報》10日在頭版刊登題為「豬肉還是少吃為好」的文章。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，受非洲豬瘟影響，中國豬農擔心損失而不養豬，導致豬肉太貴吃不起，而中央到地方政府正密集推出穩定肉價的措施；文章還引述營養師意見呼籲，大量吃豬肉對身體不好，民眾應改變飲食習慣，少吃豬肉，多吃白肉。<br />\n<br />\n對此，1名來自湖北的李姓家庭婦女感到不以為然，痛批該文章愚弄老百姓，「這樣的文章，誤導和引導老百姓朝另1方向去想。中國上下5000年的歷史，權貴一直把老百姓當成愚民對待。當它物資需求充沛，需要你的貨幣，就拼命鼓吹老百姓去買；當它物資缺乏的時候，就鼓吹物資不好，以達到他們的目的」。<br />\n<br />\n李女士表示，受到非洲豬瘟影響，湖北老家的畜牧業幾乎陷於停頓，擔心豬肉價格還會繼續上升，春節之前恐無希望吃到便宜的豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2913486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2913486&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=cae77253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2913486&h=8e09f70f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2913486</a>"},{"pid":"7e49a84b1aa98dc2c1a7fb1c5a3011fe7d289a1c","tid":1562160,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3876a51480def5376221f8edc24b2261534d5a8b","tid":1562160,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:05:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f79bdfd526b7a57b62723a2817a71b40d2692f89","tid":1562160,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f508ad62f60917e0083b7fe535869d3fb7b48e6d","tid":1562160,"uid":42429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"之前唔係禁人養豬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed89b9ff1d8c50bd091e76659affcbe9c466eea5","tid":1562160,"uid":140552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"啱呀 講好貿易戰行先 食草同樹皮最有營養"},{"pid":"ac4c456ed11fc340fbff833e95f66d9ef8e409ce","tid":1562160,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"吃草的10個好處 震驚了十四億人"}]}